name: BetaPro Canadian Gold Miners -2x Daily Bear ETF
longDescription: GDXD seeks daily investment results, before fees, expenses, distributions, brokerage commissions and other transaction costs, that endeavour to correspond to two times (200 percent) the inverse (opposite) of the daily performance of the Solactive Canadian Gold Miners Index. GDXD does not seek to achieve its stated investment objective over a period of time greater than one day.
